    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How do I book a lab?</summary>
        <p>You must be logged on to your DLSU account, then select a lab and date (up to 7 days in advance), choose available seats and timeslots, and click reserve slot.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How do I update my profile?</summary>
        <p>Log in, click your profile icon in the top right, choose "Account Settings," then "Edit Profile."</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What happens when I'm late for my reservation?</summary>
        <p>Lab technicians may cancel your reservation 10 minutes before the time if you don’t show up.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How do I see available slots?</summary>
        <p>Available slots for the next 7 days can be viewed on the calendar on the dashboard.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>

